  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An explanation from the police about the removal of protesters from the President's office",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Media Spokesman Division has made an explanation regarding the operation carried out by the security forces in the early hours of today to evacuate the people who were staying at the Presidential Secretariat.",
        "The division mentions that the protesters were told to leave on several occasions, but they remained there on different dates.",
        "Also, the peace-loving party questioned the police for not removing these protesters and the police will take appropriate measures to protect public order."
      ],
